    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h2 id=\"QZIntegratedPrinting-StartHere!-WhatisIntegratedPrinting?\">What is Integrated Printing?</h2><p>RepairQ utilizes QZ Tray integration for seamless printing without navigating print dialogs. This provides users with a one-click printing process for receipts, invoices, and labels directly to their assigned printer. Users can also create and customize print automation for a hands-free process for printing, further streamlining your ticket workflow.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Effortless Printing</strong> - Skip the hassle of print dialogs and save time by generating receipts, invoices, and labels, through a single-click process.</p></li><li><p><strong>Streamlined Workflow</strong> - Automated Printing saves time and effort by reducing manual printing tasks and creating a smoother experience for the user and customer.</p></li><li><p><strong>Personalized Print Automation</strong> - Customize automation by directing different document types to specific printers (receipt, desk, label).</p></li></ul><p>Before installing QZ Tray, make sure all of your computers using this integration meet the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936588827\" rel=\"nofollow\">Minimum System Requirements</a>. Once you have verified, continue below for setup resources.</p><p /><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"block\" href=\"https://youtu.be/RkArxhj2q68\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/RkArxhj2q68</a><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934229707/image-20230608-183334.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"QZIntegratedPrinting-StartHere!-IntegratedPrintingResources\">Integrated Printing Resources</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.servicecentral.com/products/repair-q/hardware-recommendations/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RepairQ Recommended Hardware</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936588827\" rel=\"nofollow\">QZ Tray Printing System Requirement and Printer Settings</a></p><h2 id=\"QZIntegratedPrinting-StartHere!-IntegratedPrintingsetup\">Integrated Printing setup</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936359430\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrated Printing 101: Downloading QZ Tray</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936457750\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrated Printing 102: Adding Integrated Printers</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936949270\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrated Printing 103: Adding and Assigning Printer Configurations</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936392218\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrated Printing 104: Creating and Customizing Print Automation</a></p><h2 id=\"QZIntegratedPrinting-StartHere!-IntegratedPrintingTroubleshooting\">Integrated Printing Troubleshooting</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936949301\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrated Printing Troubleshooting</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
